data.oai_dc:dc: This file contains all of the supplementary figures from the study "Evaluating the Impact of Genomic Data and Priors on Bayesian Estimates of the Angiosperm Evolutionary Timescale". In total, there are 52 supplementary figures within. Of these, 48 are tree files (five phylograms, four rategrams, 39 chronograms) that can be read in FigTree or a similar program. There is also a PDF with figure captions for each of the supplementary figures.
